Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.87,0:01:09.25,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to go to the unbelievable world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.87,0:01:09.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,arienai sekai wo iku nara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:13.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,your toughness, that’s what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:13.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kimi no tafunesu sore ga hitsuyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:16.76,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Being brazen, is it a crime?
