Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.93,0:01:19.93,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanted->means Winner:D
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.93,0:01:19.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shimeitehai->tsumari Winner
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.85,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Freedom is our only rule
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jiyuu dakega ore tachi no ruuru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:30.94,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not our way to worry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:30.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinpai nante dokofuku kaze--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:33.48,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,At any cost, One Piece, I’ll be the first
