Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.48,0:01:37.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume miru kokoro wa choo dekai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.48,0:01:37.53,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,My dreaming heart is huge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:41.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,samenai koto ga daiji--
