Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:02.76,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We go...to where the dream is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:07.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dare mo oitekanaize--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:07.85,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We won’t left anyone behind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:10.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nshin aru nomi sore ga chikai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:10.48,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going forward, that’s our pledge
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:14.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume ga hajimatta ano hi kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:14.23,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the day that the dream began
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:18.57,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,mezasu mirai wa onaji--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:18.57,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,the future that I’m \Naiming at hasn’t changed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:21.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:21.32,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
