Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:28.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:28.58,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:32.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:32.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:39.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:39.97,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:44.18,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, the \Nsecond half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,except for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.40,0:03:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.33,0:03:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.18,0:03:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy whose body turned to rubber \Nafter he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.57,0:03:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After surviving a fierce battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Straw Hats finally \Nentered the New World,--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the harshest sea ruled by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.47,0:03:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does he mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to help us! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.34,0:03:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After being taken to a
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,mysterious facility by an \Nunknown group of people,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.43,0:03:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami and the others encountered \Nstrange children.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.95,0:03:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's help these children!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.78,0:04:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Nami-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know for sure they need saving!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just met them and we don't \Nknow what's going on here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.71,0:04:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not our job to help every single person!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand what you're saying but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.01,0:04:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you can't turn your back \Non a child crying for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you get away! Wait, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.68,0:04:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That centaur again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.43,0:04:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The intruders are going that \Nway! Please finish them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see a man with swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.80,0:04:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So is that the samurai who cut our people?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snow! Snow! I love playing with snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-dah! Snowmen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.93,0:05:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.44,0:05:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Swordplay Showdown! Brook vs. \Nthe Mysterious Torso Samurai!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.17,0:05:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how far we go, all \Nwe see is a wall of ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:06:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no point in protecting ourselves \Nfrom the gas if we can't land.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up yet. Keep searching.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.64,0:06:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An eruption?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.67,0:06:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Around here, it feels like...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.32,0:06:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we are being watched by Akainu and Aokiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.08,0:06:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, that's scary!\N--Let's go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Breaking the surface won't help...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a river!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey hey, that was amazing, Smo-yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.01,0:07:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know there was a \Nriver behind there, Smo-yan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah, Smo-yan?!\N--I didn't notice it at all, Smo-yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.57,0:08:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell by looking at the sea current!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.38,0:08:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to pay attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ought to check your own behavior too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.89,0:08:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.91,0:08:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The important thing is not the \Nfact that there was a river.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.27,0:08:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is whether the ice that \Nwas blocking the river mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was natural or man-made.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean  somebody was \Nhiding the river on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would wanna live on such an \Nisland filled with the poison gas?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.23,0:08:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous! No one \Nwants to live with a mask on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the man on the Snail \Nmentioned the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably misheard it, Tashigi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.74,0:08:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even a Transponder \NSnail could survive here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.87,0:08:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.19,0:08:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have time for laughing,  \Nbreak up more ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What the hell?!\N--A wall of ice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.01,0:09:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we collide into it,  even \Nthis warship would sink!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh no!\N--We gotta destroy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:22.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,PUNK HAZARD ISLAND - THE \NMIDDLE LAKE LUFFY'S GROUP
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! Please take care of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:43.30,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Brownbeard-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:49.40,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE BOSS – BROWNBEARD - AN ALLIGATOR CENTAUR\N(A FORMER PIRATE,  BOUNTY: 80 MILLION 60 THOUSAND BERRIES)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:46.48,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,will kick your asses all the way to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.47,0:09:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all centaurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they wanna join us too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.05,0:09:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:10:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're obviously prepared to fight us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're colleagues of the man who sent \Nout the emergency signal, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they must be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to clear the air \Nbefore they start to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.18,0:10:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here to help you \Npeople! Let's talk first!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying through your teeth!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're with the samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So there's no doubt that you're intruders!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Samurai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.01,0:10:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's talking about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's not a samurai - he's a swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.92,0:10:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a dumb meathead who picks fights \Nwithout thinking sometimes but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he's not the one who attacked your people!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.51,0:10:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did you call "dumb"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help! He's gonna kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm not gonna kill you! Stop saying that!\N--They're having a falling out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.81,0:10:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pathetic ploy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let them go any further! Shoot them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.08,0:10:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:09.52,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE ICE LANDS - INSIDE OF THE \NMYSTERIOUS FACILITY NAMI'S GROUP
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.85,0:11:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, kids! Run if you wanna get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're on fire, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.78,0:11:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.98,0:11:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji entrusted me with \Nthe important mission of
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,protecting the kids and \Ngetting them out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll carry it through!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.02,0:11:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are those kids running?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a man! Leave it up to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, racoon bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.37,0:12:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a raccoon - I'm a reindeer! Hi-ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.25,0:12:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But where should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's something you need \Nto figure out. Wachaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, are we going to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! We've been though \Nsituations like this lots of times!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So just relax and follow us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.02,0:12:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.77,0:12:33.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE MYSTERIOUS FACILITY - \NBISCUIT ROOM SANJI'S GROUP
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.06,0:12:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weapons Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.69,0:12:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has weapons all over his body!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who broke the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You guys wanna know more about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.69,0:13:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'll spend as much \Ntime with you as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.22,0:13:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Load the poison gas canisters! \NThere are no kids in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire at will!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you take off your mask \Nand smoke some poison gas with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He ripped off our masks!\N--He broke our air tanks too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't use gas canisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheep?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.48,0:13:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one is different from the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.44,0:13:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he? He's proving an able opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:14:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's what's going on with my torso!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.38,0:14:11.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,IN FRONT OF THE MYSTERIOUS FACILITY BROOK
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.66,0:14:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is your head and legs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're scaring me! Please say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.69,0:15:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll reach the end of the river soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what will be there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a ghost, by any chance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, you gotta obey the rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come out during the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.70,0:15:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.73,0:15:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just set foot on the \Nisland to make snowmen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, would you like to join \Nme and make one, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can make a snow sculpture as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.09,0:16:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can he attack me with such precision?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't have eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.65,0:16:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! I don't have eyes, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary! He's strong! Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.07,0:16:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you just tell me \Nwhy you wanna fight me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aubade Coup Droit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.97,0:16:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two-Sword Style?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.78,0:17:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary! Scary! Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you catch the escapees?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I have news about G-5.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.76,0:17:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The poison gas didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.66,0:17:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, they are breaking \Nthrough ice floes with a cannon
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and slowly forcing their way into the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.45,0:17:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll reach the laboratory in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.03,0:18:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.82,0:18:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do they want to come \Ninto the island so badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.61,0:18:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do they know something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is in charge?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral Smoker.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.02,0:18:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoker?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.85,0:18:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all others, that pain in the neck?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.77,0:18:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conceal all the ships moored at the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna deal with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.91,0:18:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's allowed to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.07,0:18:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them find you at any cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.85,0:18:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'll deal with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous! I can't \Njust show myself like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.52,0:18:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is no one else who can stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.56,0:19:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.21,0:19:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've only just landed on the island. Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.03,0:19:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so harsh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.15,0:19:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did our best so be kind to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.84,0:19:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be such a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoker-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.76,0:19:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--There is no gas.\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.47,0:20:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to believe but she's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why was there poison gas earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.29,0:20:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody who doesn't want to \Nwelcome us released it probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.76,0:20:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.02,0:20:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Dr. Vegapunk's laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.66,0:20:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Former laboratory, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be abandoned and empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.37,0:20:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is still power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.94,0:20:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is living here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's taking you so long?! \NAre you afraid of us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.46,0:20:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have to ring a doorbell and wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.95,0:20:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can just break the door with \Nthe cannon of the ship, Smo-yan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.26,0:20:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoker-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:21:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey! Answer!\N--Just open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.56,0:21:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.09,0:21:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is allowed to be here on this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever you are, you're under arrest, fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.01,0:21:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.82,0:21:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ignoring us? Okay, bring the cannon here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let's put a big hole in it!\N--Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.29,0:21:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It opened!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.63,0:21:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're giving up? We're the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.93,0:21:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What brought you here - to my vacation home?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,White Chase-ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.10,0:21:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.05,0:21:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.34,0:22:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He used to be a rookie with a 440 \Nmillion berry bounty and now,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.29,0:22:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he is among them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.30,0:22:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,..."Hawk-Eye" Mihawk, Pirate \NEmpress Boa Hancock,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.57,0:22:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Don Quixote Doflamingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.63,0:22:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates backed by the World Government -
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.64,0:22:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Seven Warlords!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.28,0:22:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trafalgar Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.77,0:22:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back, Smoker-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.84,0:22:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want anything to do with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.69,0:22:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what he did!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.68,0:22:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To become a member of the Warlords...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.06,0:22:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he delivered the hearts of one \Nhundred pirates to the headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.33,0:22:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.06,0:22:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a creep!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.61,0:23:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.76,0:23:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one, not even pirates \Nor Government allies,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.61,0:23:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is allowed to be here on this island, Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.47,0:23:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means you people \Nare not allowed, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.56,0:23:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law stands in Smoker's way,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.21,0:23:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and neither will yield a single step.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.28,0:23:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the situation reaches its boiling point,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.72,0:23:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Straw Hat Pirates suddenly \Nappear with the children in tow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.83,0:23:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was then that Law does something that causes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.48,0:23:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the situation to move immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.89,0:23:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.43,0:23:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Swordplay Showdown! Brook vs. \Nthe Mysterious Torso Samurai!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.52,0:23:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
